Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go tomorrow, but we'll be there\Nsometime around the third of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's talk about it again when we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah... I'm am busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging up. Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the year is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the new year buckwheat noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What did mom say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she's looking forward on our visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Also to hurry and let her see her grandchild's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're already showing this movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed that this movie became a big hit in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They made good commercials of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been watching on TV lately, Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Do you want to see this movie together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you not to fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we going to see the first sunrise of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, I'm just taking a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that but you always\Nend up sleeping til morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, just wake me up when morning comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll already be late by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... It's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This will keep you awake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be bad, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that it's about time already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Having a baby, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well... I want one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, should we go in our bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... I just started feeling nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not weird, feeling like this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hips up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's steadily dripping out so much from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I already want your thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sou-kun... Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it next...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You already did it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cute down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you about to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi, are you feeling cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving me warmth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're warm as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come a lot inside me tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:12:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Let's make a bunch of kids, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bear lots and lots
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of children for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want plenty of children?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That we should make a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Isn't it merrier to have a larger family?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I remember, you're an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have a boy first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to be as handsome as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer one that resembles you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weird.
